snippet.title: Failing in Exchanging Note from Bank, Youth Commits Suicide in Bulandshahr

localized.description:
After failing in exchanging note of Rs 1000 at bank, youth commits suicide in Bulandshahr. His family members said that Modi government should continue fight against corruption and black money.
